title: The Saturdays- Not Giving Up- EP
description:
The new 2014 EP from The Saturdays in 320kbps! Unfortunately I'm missing a track (the TKNIK Remix) due to file corruption issues and iTunes is being a bitch. Enjoy my 1st upload ever!

TRACKLIST

1. Not Giving Up (Extended 12" Version)

2. Bigger (Not Giving Up B-Side)

3. Not Giving Up (Cahill Radio Remix)

4. What About Us (Acoustic Live From Transmitter Studios 2014)

SEED AND ENJOY!
